Ball bouncing game
- ball must bounce when interracting with wall (mandatory)
- ball must bounce when interracting with obstacle (mandatory)
- must have user mouse input (mandatory)
- items for the ball to interact with (optional)
- ball should change color on each touch (optional)
- ball speed increases every bounce (optional)

Driving game
- Must have user keyboard input (mandatory)
- Vehicle move forward without input (mandatory)
- Game must end when car hits an obstacle (mandatory)
- player has set amount of lives (optional)
- player can grab upgrades when dodging obstacles (optional)
- player can make it to a finish line (optional)
- vehicle gets faster after every avoided obstacles (optional)
